{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 459.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I collected a beautiful bouquet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did find something strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As I was climbing that hill, that there were huge chunks of bones sticking out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know what to think, nor did I understand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I did notice that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got back to the barrack, and I said to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Changeri, here, I want to thank you for taking care of us-- beautiful wildflowers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, oh, very pretty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where did you get them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, I went up to that U-shaped hill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were right on the top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I wanted to climb all the way to the top just to bring them to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said, don't you ever go back there again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She said, well, don't you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is a hill that was created when the Minsk Nazis-- Minsk in Belarussia-- were running out of ammunition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They gathered the people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they ran out of bullets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they buried them alive and watched them for three days and nights.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "These hills were going up and down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know if she found out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Interestingly enough, she was right, because I read about a book by John Loftus, and it talks about the situation in some of the ghettos in Belarussia where they could not have enough ammunition.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people were buried alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I learned another little aspect of the Holocaust story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To me, that was something new I didn't know about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed there for about-- the big interesting thing was there that there were a lot of other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I remember Italians who  were held in that camp, were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would be very interested in entertaining and singing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
